<p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/repositories_localcopy/OKCS/Trunk/CustomerPortal/topicrefs/c_Replace_search.php_aa1155853.dita" xtrc="p:5;24:4">Hereâ€™s an example of the reference implementation results page:</p>
<codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/D:/repositories_localcopy/OKCS/Trunk/CustomerPortal/topicrefs/c_Replace_search.php_aa1155853.dita" xtrc="codeblock:1;25:12">&lt;rn:meta title="#rn:msg:FIND_ANS_HDG#" template="okcs_standard.php" clickstream="answer_list"/&gt;
